[{"text": "This story", "start": 15.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is about taking imagination seriously.", "start": 17.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Fourteen years ago,", "start": 20.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I first encountered this ordinary material, fishnet,", "start": 22.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "used the same way for centuries.", "start": 25.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Today, I'm using it to create", "start": 28.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "permanent, billowing, voluptuous forms", "start": 30.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the scale of hard-edged buildings", "start": 33.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in cities around the world.", "start": 35.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I was an unlikely person to be doing this.", "start": 38.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I never studied sculpture,", "start": 41.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "engineering or architecture.", "start": 43.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "In fact, after college", "start": 45.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I applied to seven art schools", "start": 47.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and was rejected by all seven.", "start": 49.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I went off on my own to become an artist,", "start": 53.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I painted for 10 years,", "start": 55.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "when I was offered a Fulbright to India.", "start": 59.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Promising to give exhibitions of paintings,", "start": 62.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I shipped my paints and arrived in Mahabalipuram.", "start": 65.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "The deadline for the show arrived --", "start": 67.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "my paints didn't.", "start": 70.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I had to do something.", "start": 72.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This fishing village was famous for sculpture.", "start": 74.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So I tried bronze casting.", "start": 76.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But to make large forms was too heavy and expensive.", "start": 79.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I went for a walk on the beach,", "start": 82.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "watching the fishermen", "start": 84.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "bundle their nets into mounds on the sand.", "start": 86.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I'd seen it every day,", "start": 88.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but this time I saw it differently --", "start": 90.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a new approach to sculpture,", "start": 92.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a way to make volumetric form", "start": 94.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "without heavy solid materials.", "start": 97.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "My first satisfying sculpture", "start": 100.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "was made in collaboration with these fishermen.", "start": 102.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It's a self-portrait", "start": 105.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "titled \"Wide Hips.\"", "start": 107.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 109.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We hoisted them on poles to photograph.", "start": 113.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I discovered", "start": 116.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "their soft surfaces", "start": 118.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "revealed every ripple of wind", "start": 120.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in constantly changing patterns.", "start": 122.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I was mesmerized.", "start": 124.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I continued studying craft traditions", "start": 127.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and collaborating with artisans,", "start": 130.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "next in Lithuania with lace makers.", "start": 132.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I liked the fine detail", "start": 134.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "it gave my work,", "start": 136.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but I wanted to make them larger --", "start": 138.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to shift from being an object you look at", "start": 140.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to something you could get lost in.", "start": 142.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Returning to India to work with those fishermen,", "start": 145.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we made a net", "start": 148.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of a million and a half hand-tied knots --", "start": 150.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "installed briefly in Madrid.", "start": 155.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Thousands of people saw it,", "start": 158.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and one of them was the urbanist", "start": 160.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Manual Sola-Morales", "start": 162.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who was redesigning the waterfront", "start": 164.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in Porto, Portugal.", "start": 166.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "He asked if I could build this", "start": 169.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as a permanent piece for the city.", "start": 171.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I didn't know if I could do that", "start": 173.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and preserve my art.", "start": 175.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Durable, engineered, permanent --", "start": 177.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "those are in opposition", "start": 180.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to idiosyncratic, delicate and ephemeral.", "start": 182.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "For two years, I searched for a fiber", "start": 186.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that could survive ultraviolet rays,", "start": 189.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "salt, air, pollution,", "start": 191.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and at the same time remain soft enough", "start": 194.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to move fluidly in the wind.", "start": 196.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We needed something to hold the net up", "start": 199.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "out there in the middle of the traffic circle.", "start": 201.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So we raised this 45,000-pound steel ring.", "start": 203.26, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "We had to engineer it", "start": 208.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to move gracefully in an average breeze", "start": 210.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and survive in hurricane winds.", "start": 212.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But there was no engineering software", "start": 215.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to model something porous and moving.", "start": 218.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "I found a brilliant aeronautical engineer", "start": 222.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "who designs sails for America's Cup racing yachts", "start": 225.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "named Peter Heppel.", "start": 228.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "He helped me tackle the twin challenges", "start": 231.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of precise shape", "start": 233.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and gentle movement.", "start": 235.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I couldn't build this the way I knew", "start": 238.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "because hand-tied knots", "start": 240.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "weren't going to withstand a hurricane.", "start": 242.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So I developed a relationship", "start": 244.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "with an industrial fishnet factory,", "start": 246.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "learned the variables of their machines,", "start": 248.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and figured out a way", "start": 250.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to make lace with them.", "start": 252.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "There was no language", "start": 255.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to translate this ancient, idiosyncratic handcraft", "start": 257.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "into something machine operators could produce.", "start": 261.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So we had to create one.", "start": 264.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Three years and two children later,", "start": 267.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "we raised this 50,000-square-foot lace net.", "start": 271.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It was hard to believe", "start": 274.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that what I had imagined", "start": 276.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "was now built, permanent", "start": 278.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and had lost nothing in translation.", "start": 281.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 284.26, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "This intersection had been bland and anonymous.", "start": 289.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Now it had a sense of place.", "start": 292.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I walked underneath it", "start": 295.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for the first time.", "start": 297.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "As I watched the wind's choreography unfold,", "start": 299.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I felt sheltered", "start": 302.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and, at the same time,", "start": 304.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "connected to limitless sky.", "start": 306.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "My life was not going to be the same.", "start": 308.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I want to create these oases of sculpture", "start": 319.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in spaces of cities around the world.", "start": 322.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I'm going to share two directions", "start": 325.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that are new in my work.", "start": 327.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Historic Philadelphia City Hall:", "start": 330.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "its plaza, I felt, needed a material for sculpture", "start": 332.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "that was lighter than netting.", "start": 336.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So we experimented", "start": 338.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "with tiny atomized water particles", "start": 340.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to create a dry mist", "start": 342.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that is shaped by the wind", "start": 344.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and in testing, discovered", "start": 346.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that it can be shaped by people", "start": 348.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who can interact and move through it without getting wet.", "start": 350.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I'm using this sculpture material", "start": 353.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to trace the paths of subway trains above ground", "start": 356.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "in real time --", "start": 360.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "like an X-ray of the city's circulatory system unfolding.", "start": 363.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Next challenge,", "start": 371.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the Biennial of the Americas in Denver", "start": 373.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "asked, could I represent", "start": 375.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the 35 nations of the Western hemisphere and their interconnectedness", "start": 377.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in a sculpture?", "start": 380.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 382.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I didn't know where to begin,", "start": 385.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but I said yes.", "start": 387.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I read about the recent earthquake in Chile", "start": 389.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and the tsunami that rippled across", "start": 392.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the entire Pacific Ocean.", "start": 394.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It shifted the Earth's tectonic plates,", "start": 396.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "sped up the planet's rotation", "start": 399.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and literally shortened the length of the day.", "start": 401.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So I contacted NOAA,", "start": 404.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and I asked if they'd share their data on the tsunami,", "start": 407.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and translated it into this.", "start": 410.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Its title: \"1.26\"", "start": 415.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "refers to the number of microseconds", "start": 418.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that the Earth's day was shortened.", "start": 420.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I couldn't build this with a steel ring, the way I knew.", "start": 423.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Its shape was too complex now.", "start": 426.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So I replaced the metal armature", "start": 429.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "with a soft, fine mesh", "start": 431.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of a fiber 15 times stronger than steel.", "start": 433.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "The sculpture could now be entirely soft,", "start": 437.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "which made it so light", "start": 441.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "it could tie in to existing buildings --", "start": 443.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "literally becoming part of the fabric of the city.", "start": 446.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "There was no software", "start": 449.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that could extrude these complex net forms", "start": 451.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and model them with gravity.", "start": 454.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So we had to create it.", "start": 456.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Then I got a call from New York City", "start": 459.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "asking if I could adapt these concepts", "start": 462.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to Times Square", "start": 465.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "or the High Line.", "start": 467.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This new soft structural method", "start": 469.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "enables me to model these", "start": 472.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and build these sculptures", "start": 474.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "at the scale of skyscrapers.", "start": 476.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "They don't have funding yet,", "start": 479.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but I dream now", "start": 481.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of bringing these to cities around the world", "start": 483.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "where they're most needed.", "start": 486.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Fourteen years ago,", "start": 489.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I searched for beauty", "start": 492.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in the traditional things,", "start": 495.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in craft forms.", "start": 497.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Now I combine them with hi-tech materials and engineering", "start": 502.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "to create voluptuous, billowing forms", "start": 506.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the scale of buildings.", "start": 509.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "My artistic horizons continue to grow.", "start": 512.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I'll leave you with this story.", "start": 515.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I got a call from a friend in Phoenix.", "start": 518.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "An attorney in the office", "start": 521.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who'd never been interested in art,", "start": 523.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "never visited the local art museum,", "start": 525.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "dragged everyone she could from the building", "start": 528.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and got them outside to lie down underneath the sculpture.", "start": 531.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "There they were in their business suits,", "start": 534.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "laying in the grass,", "start": 536.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "noticing the changing patterns of wind", "start": 538.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "beside people they didn't know,", "start": 540.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "sharing the rediscovery of wonder.", "start": 542.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Thank you.", "start": 546.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 548.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Thank you. Thank you.", "start": 551.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Thank you.", "start": 553.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Thank you. Thank you.", "start": 555.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 558.26, "duration": 2.0}]